column5: Hi everyone,  Please help me decide between Canal lake and Dalrymple lake.  If you had a day to fish, which of the 2 would you pick?  Thanks for any help
For a day fishing!  Dalrymple for sure.   Rick

I appreciate the reply Rick.  I did a search on the 2 lakes and I've decided to try dalrymple lake.  Not keeping any of the fish so I'll be happy with catching a few hammer handle pike and bass if I'm lucky.
You might even find a Walleye or 2.  Rick
